---
title: Error Handling Flow
description: Error handling and propagation flow across application layers
author: Tech Team
date: 2025-11-06
---

```mermaid
graph TD
    %% Frontend Layer
    User[👤 User Action]
    FrontendCatch[🎨 Frontend Catches Error]
    DisplayError[💬 Display User-Friendly Message]

    %% API Layer
    APIEndpoint[🔌 API Endpoint]
    APIErrorHandler[🛡️ API Error Handler]
    MapHTTPStatus[🔢 Map to HTTP Status]

    %% Service Layer
    ServiceMethod[⚙️ Service Method]
    ServiceCatch[🎯 Service Catches Error]
    ServiceOutput[📦 ServiceOutput<br/>success: false<br/>error: ErrorCode]

    %% Model Layer
    ModelMethod[🗃️ Model Method]
    ModelCatch[🎯 Model Catches SQL Error]
    TransformError[🔄 Transform to ModelError]

    %% Database Layer
    Database[(🗄️ PostgreSQL)]
    SQLError[❌ SQL Error]

    %% Error Flow
    User -->|Request| APIEndpoint
    APIEndpoint -->|Call| ServiceMethod
    ServiceMethod -->|Call| ModelMethod
    ModelMethod -->|Query| Database
    Database -->|Throws| SQLError

    SQLError -->|Caught by| ModelCatch
    ModelCatch -->|Transform| TransformError
    TransformError -->|Return| ServiceCatch
    ServiceCatch -->|Wrap| ServiceOutput
    ServiceOutput -->|Return| APIErrorHandler
    APIErrorHandler -->|Map| MapHTTPStatus
    MapHTTPStatus -->|Response| FrontendCatch
    FrontendCatch -->|Show| DisplayError
    DisplayError -->|Feedback| User

    %% Error Types by Layer
    subgraph DatabaseErrors[Database Layer Errors]
        DBUnique[Unique Constraint<br/>23505]
        DBForeignKey[Foreign Key<br/>23503]
        DBNotNull[Not Null<br/>23502]
        DBConnection[Connection Error]
    end

    subgraph ModelErrors[Model Layer Errors]
        ModelNotFound[NOT_FOUND]
        ModelDuplicate[DUPLICATE_ENTRY]
        ModelInvalid[INVALID_DATA]
    end

    subgraph ServiceErrors[Service Layer Errors]
        ValidationError[VALIDATION_ERROR]
        NotFoundError[NOT_FOUND]
        UnauthorizedError[UNAUTHORIZED]
        ForbiddenError[FORBIDDEN]
        BusinessError[BUSINESS_LOGIC_ERROR]
        InternalError[INTERNAL_ERROR]
    end

    subgraph HTTPStatus[HTTP Status Codes]
        Status400[400 Bad Request]
        Status401[401 Unauthorized]
        Status403[403 Forbidden]
        Status404[404 Not Found]
        Status409[409 Conflict]
        Status500[500 Internal Server Error]
    end

    subgraph UserMessages[User-Friendly Messages]
        Msg400[Invalid input data]
        Msg401[Please log in]
        Msg403[Access denied]
        Msg404[Resource not found]
        Msg409[Already exists]
        Msg500[Something went wrong]
    end

    %% Error Mapping
    DBUnique -.->|Transform| ModelDuplicate
    DBForeignKey -.->|Transform| ModelNotFound
    DBNotNull -.->|Transform| ModelInvalid
    DBConnection -.->|Transform| InternalError

    ModelNotFound -.->|Wrap| NotFoundError
    ModelDuplicate -.->|Wrap| ValidationError
    ModelInvalid -.->|Wrap| ValidationError

    ValidationError -.->|Map| Status400
    UnauthorizedError -.->|Map| Status401
    ForbiddenError -.->|Map| Status403
    NotFoundError -.->|Map| Status404
    BusinessError -.->|Map| Status409
    InternalError -.->|Map| Status500

    Status400 -.->|Display| Msg400
    Status401 -.->|Display| Msg401
    Status403 -.->|Display| Msg403
    Status404 -.->|Display| Msg404
    Status409 -.->|Display| Msg409
    Status500 -.->|Display| Msg500

    %% Styling
    classDef frontend fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1e40af,color:#fff
    classDef api fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,color:#fff
    classDef service fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#d97706,color:#fff
    classDef model fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#fff
    classDef database fill:#ef4444,stroke:#dc2626,color:#fff
    classDef error fill:#ec4899,stroke:#db2777,color:#fff

    class User,FrontendCatch,DisplayError frontend
    class APIEndpoint,APIErrorHandler,MapHTTPStatus api
    class ServiceMethod,ServiceCatch,ServiceOutput service
    class ModelMethod,ModelCatch,TransformError model
    class Database,SQLError database
    class DBUnique,DBForeignKey,DBNotNull,DBConnection,ModelNotFound,ModelDuplicate,ModelInvalid,ValidationError,NotFoundError,UnauthorizedError,ForbiddenError,BusinessError,InternalError error
```
